featured_reviews.review_id:
Alhamdulillah. Ma Sha Allah. Subhan Allah. Maza hi aa gya. Peace and happiness. Allah blessed me and my wife to pray in such a beautiful mosque. The Imam sahab was so humble. There is a separate ladies hall for prayer with basin and washroom. Also, there are holy books available in ladies hall too. It was really a nice experience. Although I didn't find Ooty to be so beautiful but on the last day of my trip, I was blessed to pray some rakaats of namaz in this holy mosque. Alhamdulillah.

Also u can have hot water to drink anytime of the day and outside, there are 2-3 non-veg restaurants with halaal food. Biryani and chicken kebab(fry) is a must try there .
